Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:09.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:11.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,今天也有工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:15.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,今天難得大家會聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,中午過後就需要趕去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.89,0:24:19.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,下午的筆記拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:20.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.10,0:24:22.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,我會提供容易抄寫的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:24.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:25.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:26.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:27.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:28.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.23,0:24:30.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,聽說今天要集合在一起了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:31.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:33.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,我都等不及了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.39,0:24:59.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,那一天 在心中結下的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.35,0:25:02.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,依舊如昔日一樣緊密
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.35,0:25:04.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.23,0:25:07.06,Faqi,,0,0,1,,Yes, my master.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}是 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:08.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光戰斧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.02,0:25:09.74,Faqi,,0,0,1,,Yes, sir.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}是 主人
